public java.lang.String showHomePage(@AuthenticationPrincipal
                                                             MyUserDetails userConnected,

        Parameters:
        model - to pass data to the view.
        userConnected - is the authenticated User passed within the object MyUserDetails
        Returns:
        index.html

      • showUserConnectedHomePage

public java.lang.String showUserConnectedHomePage(@AuthenticationPrincipal
